    'published' => 1436425200,
    'title' => 'TED Talks to save you time at work',
    'link' => 'http://www.blogger.com/feeds/4058815900324538230/posts/default/1201587174133846248',
    'link2' => '2015/07/ted-talks-to-save-you-time-at-work',
    'article' => '<p>It\'s always good to have a few short-cuts to hand that save your a few seconds here and there - they\'ll soon add up to a nice time saving and will make tedious tasks less frustrating.</p>
<p>Here are a few TED Talks that will help you save time at work:</p>
